<div class="title">Discovering the Land of Faery</div>
<div class="substance">Cacti - T. peruvianus</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=San+Pedro&Exact=1">San Pedro</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; San Pedro. "Discovering the Land of Faery: An Experience with Cacti - T. peruvianus (exp18549)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 30, 2002. erowid.org/exp/18549</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
